      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:8:55:3",
      "text": [
        " خَرَجَ إِلَيَّ أَبُو الْحَسَنِ ( عليه السلام ) فَوَجَدْتُ مِنْهُ رَائِحَةَ التَّجْمِيرِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Abu Abdullah, from Musa Bin Al Qasim, from Ali Bin Asbaat, from Al Hassan Bin Jahm who said, ",
          "‘Abu Al-Hassan<sup>asws</sup> came out to me, so I found from him<sup>asws</sup> an aroma of <span class=\"iTxt\">Al-Tajmeer</span> (incense)’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "3. A number of our people have narrated from Ahmad ibn abu ‘Abd Allah from Musa ibn al-Qasim from Ali ibn Asbat from al-Hassan ibn Jahm who has said the following: “Once abu al-Hassan, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, came out and I felt the fragrance of incense from him (the Imam).”’ "
        ]
      }
    }
